message.content:
cs.CL, cs.CV, cs.HC, cs.IR, cs.MM

Reasoning: 
- cs.CL (Computation and Language) is the most likely category as the paper focuses on natural language processing and analyzing verbal content in job interviews.
- cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition) is also likely as the paper discusses the automatic detection of social signals in videos of job interviews.
- cs.HC (Human-Computer Interaction) is another possible category as the paper aims to design interactive systems to help candidates practice job interviews and to assist recruiters in the hiring process.
- cs.IR (Information Retrieval) is a possible category as the paper discusses modeling contextual information from job positions to improve the analysis of job interviews.
- cs.MM (Multimedia) is also a possible category as the paper deals with analyzing audio and video data from job interviews.
